document.full_text: an earthquake with a magnitude of 6.1 struck off the coast of eastern japan early on friday, the u.s. geological survey said. but there were no immediate reports of any casualties or damage.
document.title: magnitude 6.1 quake strikes off japan: u.s. geological survey
